cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with semantic and motion segmentation using deep convolutional networks. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the application of the proposed approach in outdoor robotic navigation. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses joint learning methods to extract spatio-temporal features. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes an approach to enhance the overall perception of dynamic scenes. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the fusion of semantic and motion features using optical flow.
